Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Haruka's Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This program will introduce the friends that appear in Kotoura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Kotoura Haruka, will make the introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Our guest for today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is known as the "ESP researcher"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and is the president of the ESP Research Society at Midorigaoka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please welcome Mifune Yuriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a second-year student at Midorigaoka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mifune Yuriko, the president of the ESP Research Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me here, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're the founder of the ESP Research Society, President Mifune.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the reason behind creating the ESP Research Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it because I wanted to study ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to meet a person who really has ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I get to take part in the club activities as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other people in this world who have ESP just like you, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are a few fakers among the bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not right to label all ESPs as fakes because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... By the way—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you {\i1}do{\i0} possess ESP,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's dangerous to display that ability in front of the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's not a trick, there's no guarantee that the result will be what people expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail, you'll be shunned and treated like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That is precisely why we need proper facilities for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,researching ESP and protecting those who have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Such government-run facilities exist in other countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am forced to say that Japan is seriously lagging behind in the ESP research department!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a few unofficial agencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let's go to commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but people with ESP—
